Lols, a lot of people are going for 200m. Dung is one of the fastest 200m skills in the game, and was the fastest to have an entire page of players with 200m on the HS page. I think it was like 1-2 months after the warped floors were released before the entire first page was filled with max xp.

Anyway, you get way more experience from teams than solo anyway. Just saying.
